      <title>比特幣交易員擺脫「減半」的影響，專注於更廣泛的市場風險</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bitcoin-traders-shrug-off-halving-focus-broader-market-risks-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到目前為止，比特幣所謂的減半事件對其價格影響不大，業內人士週一表示，加密貨幣的命運與更廣泛的金融市場情緒和地緣政治關係更為密切。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bitcoin-traders-shrug-off-halving-focus-broader-market-risks-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 15:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
